text.tspan: Anatomy of an Effective AI Prompt
"You are an R programming expert specialized in data visualization and ggplot2."
"Debug this ggplot2 code and identify why the legend colors aren't matching the data."
1) Identify what's wrong with the code, 2) Explain the underlying concept I'm
misunderstanding, 3) Show a working solution with comments."
